{\*\generator Msftedit 5.41.21.2510;}\viewkind4\uc1\pard\b\f0\fs17 V3.1\b0  - TNOC, TRETPOOL, TGRP\par
\b V3.2\b0  - TGRP, TUSR\par
\b V4.1\b0  - TUSR, TRULSIFT, TSEGCTR, TEGPTXT\par
\par
\f1\fs20 2012-01-09 / Omega2\par
- Various modifications for SSL and SEC Extensions (multiple tables added / modified)\par
\par
2012-01-26 / Omega2\par
- Misc corrections to realign with actual production model.\par
\par
2012-05-09 / Omega2\par
- Various small modifications for SSL and SEC Extensions\par
\par
2012-07-02 / Omega2\par
- Misc small corrections.\par
\par
???\par
- Addition of OneGL tables\par
\par
\lang1036 2013-04-18 / Omega 2-Phase 2A-TRA28 \par
- Addition of Dynamic Fields related tables.\par
\par
\lang1033 2013-06-05/ Omega2 Evocard: TRA03-Phase 2A\par
- Addition of Diary related fields on TUSR table\par
\par
2013-06-05/ Omega2 Evocard: TRA03-Phase 2A\par
- Addition of Diary related fields on TUSR table\par
\lang1036\par
2013-0\lang1033 6-26\lang1036 / Omega 2-Phase 2A-TRA28 \par
- Added autoincremetal for field DYNFIELD_CT for table TDYNFIELD.\par
\par
2013-06-27/ \lang1033 Omega2 Evocard: SGLA30 - Phase2A &amp; TRA03-Phase 2A\lang1036\par
- Addition of Settlement validation mode on TGRP2ESB (SGLA30)\par
- Addition of Threshold Evaluation Currency on TESB table (TRA03)\par
\par
2013-08-02/ Omega2-Phase 1B\par
- Addition of TIMESHIFT_N column in the TSITE table for balance sheet date changes\par
- Addition of TBATCHNIGHT table for batches centralization\par
\par
2013-07-31/ Omega2 Evocard: STL01-Phase 2A\par
- Add the embargo information in TCTY table\par
\par
2013-09-12 / Omega2 - 1B\par
PRDSIT_CF column added in table TBATCHNIGHT \par
\par
2013-08-02 / Omega2 - Phase1B\par
Modified column TIMESHIFT_N in TSITE table.\par
\par
2013-11-13 / Omega2 - Phase1B\par
- Added columns in TBATCHNIGHT table.\par
- Added TBATCHSSD table.\par
\par
2013-12-10/ Omega2-Phase2B-SGLA06-EST50\par
- Added TACCPAR, TSUBTRSBLOCKLIFEST, TSUBTRSESBPROP, TSUBTRSBASE, TSUBTRSASSO tables\par
- Added 11 columns in TSUBTRS table\par
\lang1033\par
\lang1036 2013-12-17/ Omega2-Phase2B-SGLA06\par
- Replaced DETTRS_CF (char(8)) by TRN_CF (char(5)) in TACCPAR table\par
\par
2013-12-17/ Omega2-Phase2B-SGLA06\par
- Added column PRS_CF (added to the primary key) on TSUBTRSBASE table\par
\par
2014-01-23/ Omega2-Phase2B-SGLA06\par
- Rename code of Transaction code (DETTRNCOD_CF) in TACCPAR and TSUBTRSBASE tables.\par
- Rename code of Transaction code 1 (DETTRNCOD1_CF), Transaction code 2 (DETTRNCOD2_CF) and Transaction code 3 (DETTRNCOD3_CF) in TSUBTRSASSO table.\par
\par
2014-10-28/Omega2-Phase2C-TAC01-B\par
- Two tables added : TTAXRUL &amp; TTAXRUL2SUBTRS\par
\par
2015/06/16 Phase 2D RET02 -  \f2\fs24 EXT-RET-811700 - Printing Account review \par
\f1\fs20 Add a table for grouping parameter TRETPAR. The grouping parameters are:\par
- a list of ledgers for which the grouping is effective (all by default)\par
- a category of contract for which the grouping is effective (all by default)\par
\lang1033\par
\lang1036 2015/09/09 Omega 2-Claims Platform \par
Add of  tables :\par
TUSRSKLLOB\par
TUSRSKLNOC\par
TUSRSKLCLMDAM\par
TUSRSKLLAG\par
\par
\pard\sb100\sa100\b 2015-10-12/Omega2-Phase2D-RET01\f2\fs24 -  Account Sending process optimization\b0\par
\pard\f1\fs20 Addition of Token table (TTOKEN)\par
\lang1033\par
\par
\lang1036 2016-01-21/ Omega2-Claim Platform\par
- Creation of a new table TEVTTHRHLD with:\par
-  EVTTHRHLDTYP_CF                         \par
-  EVTTHRHLD_M        \par
-  CREUSR_CF            \par
-  CRE_D                \par
-  LSTUPDUSR_CF         \par
-  LSTUPD_D    \par
-  TIMESTAMP       \par
      \par
2016-02-12/ Omega2-Claim Platform\par
- Creation of a new table TDISTRIBUTION\par
\par
2017-04-11 | OMEGA 2 | Change request\par
Addition of Column PSTOMGCONEND_D and EBSPSTOMGCONEND_D (datetime type for both) in TCALEND\par
\lang1033\par
\lang1036 2017/06/23 Omega 2-Claims Platform II\par
Creation of new table TEMLSIG\par
\par
2017/09/06 / Omega2- 3C Release - SPIRA 59186\par
- Creation of a new table TDBLATHTHR with:\par
- SSD_CF\par
- ESB_CF\par
- DBLATHTHR_M\par
- DBLATHTHRCUR_CF  \par
- CREUSR_CF            \par
- CRE_D                \par
- LSTUPDUSR_CF         \par
- LSTUPD_D    \par
- TIMESTAMP       \par
\par
2017/09/12 / Omega2- 3C Release - SPIRA 59186\par
- Creation of a new table TDBLATHTHRHISTO with:\par
- SSD_CF\par
- ESB_CF\par
- HISTO_ID\par
- DBLATHTHR_M\par
- DBLATHTHRCUR_CF  \par
- LSTUPDUSR_CF         \par
- LSTUPD_D    \par
- TIMESTAMP       \par
\lang1033\par
