<a:TotalSavingCurrency/>
<a:Description>{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg1252\deff0\deflang1036{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset0 Times New Roman;}}
{\*\generator Msftedit 5.41.21.2509;}\viewkind4\uc1\pard\f0\fs20 This table includes the authorized rights for a profile for an application (for each application window, a list of commands allowed for a profile)\par
}
</a:Description>
<a:Annotation>{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg1252\deff0\deflang1036{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset0 Times New Roman;}}
{\*\generator Msftedit 5.41.21.2509;}\viewkind4\uc1\pard\f0\fs20 RFR -The authorization table gives all authorizations to this profile on windows and menus of the Omega application for which the profile belongs.\par
If a window is allowed to update for a given profile, TAUTHOR contain a specific line, identified by the application, the profile and the window and the option code OPT_CF will be &quot;# SHIFT authorized.&quot;\par
}
</a:Annotation>
