<o:Table Id="o700">
<a:ObjectID>44CBF5A9-5619-4DA5-AC93-B8E364B5DA08</a:ObjectID>
<a:Name>CAT PML and capacities Table</a:Name>
<a:Code>TCATPML</a:Code>
<a:CreationDate>880027320</a:CreationDate>
<a:Creator>OME08</a:Creator>
<a:ModificationDate>1318498988</a:ModificationDate>
<a:Modifier>OME08</a:Modifier>
<a:Comment>Table des PML et capacités CAT</a:Comment>
<a:TotalSavingCurrency/>
<a:Description>{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg1252\deff0\deflang1036{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset0 Times New Roman;}}
{\*\generator Msftedit 5.41.21.2509;}\viewkind4\uc1\pard\f0\fs20 This table contains the underwriting capacity and PML accumulated according to CAT exposures (earthquakes, storms, floods).\par
Capabilities and PML are defined:\par
  - For a given country, or in some cases to a group of countries,\par
  - For a period (compared to the former subscription)\par
  - For treaties, FACS or accumulated,\par
  - For a subsidiary or for the SCOR Group.\par
\par
This information is entered by the DT or the cells responsible for administering the CAT accumulations in treaties and facs.\par
}
</a:Description>
<a:Annotation>{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg1252\deff0\deflang1036{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset0 Times New Roman;}}
{\*\generator Msftedit 5.41.21.2509;}\viewkind4\uc1\pard\f0\fs20 RFR - Table generated in BREF because it&#39;s common to treaties and facs, and subject to transfers between subsidiaries GROUP -&gt; subsidiary and subsidiaries -&gt; GROUP).\par
This table must be visible from all subsidiaries. It contains the CAT underwriting capacity and PML corresponding to an underwriting year, a subsidiary (or group), a CAT-prone country, and a type of CAT. It contains the column heading and PML TRT, FAC, and Global.\par
}
</a:Annotation>
<c:Columns>
