<o:Table Id="o622">
<a:ObjectID>6A795A00-CC20-4266-8E8C-5545361A7A6E</a:ObjectID>
<a:Name>Underwriting capacities</a:Name>
<a:Code>TUWCAP</a:Code>
<a:CreationDate>880027320</a:CreationDate>
<a:Creator>OME08</a:Creator>
<a:ModificationDate>1326895298</a:ModificationDate>
<a:Modifier>OME08</a:Modifier>
<a:Comment>Table des capacités de souscription</a:Comment>
<a:TotalSavingCurrency/>
<a:Annotation>{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg1252\deff0\deflang1036{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset0 Times New Roman;}}
{\*\generator Msftedit 5.41.21.2509;}\viewkind4\uc1\pard\f0\fs20 SO to be generated in BREF\par
This table contains the maximum capacity of underwriting for a subsidiary, an underwriting year, a branch (possibly a SoB) and a type of contract (Treaties / Facs). It may also contain a line feed (for use by FACS).\par
It is used to verify that the accumulated commitments do not exceed these capacities.\par
\par
The range of underwriting years covered by a given capacity is defined by:\par
   - Exercise&gt; CAPINCYEA_N = and &lt;= CAPEXPYEA_N CAPEXPYEA_N if informed,\par
   - Exercise&gt; = CAPINCYEA_N otherwise.\par
\par
The amounts are in thousands of units of the currency of the subsidiary.\par
}
</a:Annotation>
