<o:Table Id="o730">
<a:ObjectID>F3B1BA2E-7691-4BAA-9AA1-19C77E073BD6</a:ObjectID>
<a:Name>Tax references</a:Name>
<a:Code>TTAXREF</a:Code>
<a:CreationDate>880027320</a:CreationDate>
<a:Creator>OME08</a:Creator>
<a:ModificationDate>1326895719</a:ModificationDate>
<a:Modifier>OME08</a:Modifier>
<a:Comment>Table des taxes référencées</a:Comment>
<a:TotalSavingCurrency/>
<a:Annotation>{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg1252\deff0\deflang1036{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset0 Times New Roman;}}
{\*\generator Msftedit 5.41.21.2509;}\viewkind4\uc1\pard\f0\fs20 Table administered internally, used to control the management of taxes in FCC &amp; TRT.\par
\par
For FAC &amp; TRT use:\par
the user selects a TAXREF_CT directly TBANTEC,\par
if the tax is in TTAXREF we display its wording (changed), and the column &quot;meaning&quot; C or D (modified).\par
The user can also choose to not TAXREF_CT (not required).\par
}
</a:Annotation>
<c:Columns>
