<a:Name>Retrocession transformations</a:Name>
<a:Code>TRETTRF</a:Code>
<a:CreationDate>880027320</a:CreationDate>
<a:Creator>OME08</a:Creator>
<a:ModificationDate>1326891748</a:ModificationDate>
<a:Modifier>OME08</a:Modifier>
<a:Comment>Defines the way Assumed accounting transactions are transformed to Retroceded transactions</a:Comment>
<a:TotalSavingCurrency/>
<a:Description>{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg1252\deff0\deflang1036{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset0 Times New Roman;}}
{\*\generator Msftedit 5.41.21.2509;}\viewkind4\uc1\pard\f0\fs20 This table allows to know whether the\fs20  acceptance\fs20  transaction code must be turned back during the retro payment other than by change of suffix.\par
}
</a:Description>
