<o:Table Id="o750">
<a:ObjectID>E92EABA0-A506-41FC-B017-EA8891410636</a:ObjectID>
<a:Name>Fac Management Group</a:Name>
<a:Code>TGRPDIR</a:Code>
<a:CreationDate>880027320</a:CreationDate>
<a:Creator>OME08</a:Creator>
<a:ModificationDate>1326795269</a:ModificationDate>
<a:Modifier>OME08</a:Modifier>
<a:Comment>Fac Management Group table</a:Comment>
<a:TotalSavingCurrency/>
<a:Description>{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg1252\deff0\deflang1036{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset0 Times New Roman;}}
{\*\generator Msftedit 5.41.21.2509;}\viewkind4\uc1\pard\f0\fs20 Reference Tables of directions group for facs:\par
The direction group is deducted from thefac product(column GRPDIR_CF of TPRODUC)\par
\par
From January 2000, facs whose direction is in FACT are splitted into FACT and Non FACT based on the criterion of FACADMTYP_B of BFAC..TCONTR .\par
This splitting is done via the column GRPDIRNF_CF: it gives the value of the direction group of the Fac when the fac is Non FACT.\par
\par
Finally, for a given fac division:\par
- The direction group is deducted from the product associated with the division (product derived from the LOB and SOB)\par
- If the fac is Non FACT, that direction group is replaced by the value GRPDIRNF_CF associated with the management group obtained by the product\par
}
</a:Description>
<a:Annotation>{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg1252\deff0\deflang1036{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset0 Times New Roman;}}
{\*\generator Msftedit 5.41.21.2509;}\viewkind4\uc1\pard\f0\fs20 Table added following the evolutions on Stat/Reporting domain\par
\par
17/07/1997\par
}
</a:Annotation>
