<a:Comment>PROJECT BT
This table stores the PNA reference rates used, in the technical budget, for the correction of PNA calculated by the inventory in a simulation environment.
There will be in Reference application a new screen to view / modify the rates of PNA by segmentation group.

OBSOLETE in Omega 2.0</a:Comment>
