<a:Modifier>FRUMICM</a:Modifier>
<a:Comment>Defines the different Market Units (MU) per Country and Ledger</a:Comment>
<a:TotalSavingCurrency/>
<a:Description>{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg1252\deff0\deflang1036{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset0 Times New Roman;}}
{\*\generator Msftedit 5.41.21.2509;}\viewkind4\uc1\pard\f0\fs20 This table shows for each combination subsidiary / subledger / country, the main MU and the &quot;submarket&quot; MU. It allows to associate the MU to concepts that do not join underwriting extract (eg the field GLR with the debtor-creditor).\par
}
</a:Description>
<a:Annotation>{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg1252\deff0\deflang1036{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset0 Times New Roman;}}
{\*\generator Msftedit 5.41.21.2509;}\viewkind4\uc1\pard\f0\fs20 Created for the ticket SPOT n\&#39;b017708\par
\fs20\par
}
</a:Annotation>
