{\*\generator Msftedit 5.41.21.2509;}\viewkind4\uc1\pard\f0\fs20 2012-12-05 / Omega 2\par
New table for subsidiary/subledger extension.\par
The presence (resp. absence) of a record for a subledger means that the transaction code is usable (resp. not usable) in this subldeger.\par
\par
2012-12-17 / Omega 2\par
\f1\fs22 Unnecessary CMT_NT field removed \f0\fs20\par
}
