{\*\generator Msftedit 5.41.21.2509;}\viewkind4\uc1\pard\f0\fs20 Lists the Type of Police compatible with a given LoB. Also contains specific parameters of the \fs20 Omega \fs20 Fac module for a given LoB and a given ToP.\par
}
</a:Description>
