\par
2011-12-05 / Omega2\par
Preparation of new parameters at the subldeger level.\par
\par
2012-01-09 / Omega2\par
Added Night batch indicator (to be updated from subsidiary production site, added for access control performance reasons).\par
\par
2012-01-17 / Omega 2.0\par
Added the CONFID_B flag for Access Control on the Ledger\par
\par
2013-06-27/ \lang1033 Omega2 Evocard: TRA03-Phase 1B&#39;\lang1036\par
- Addition of Threshold Evaluation Currency (THRHLDCUR_CF) for Diary functionality.\par
\par
2017-09-22/ Omega2 Spira 61508 - phase 3C\par
- Add a new column LOCALAE_CT to indicate if the ledger can enter or load a local AE\par
0= Local AE none\par
1= Monthly local AE\par
2= quaterly local AE\par
\par
}
