{\*\generator Msftedit 5.41.21.2510;}\viewkind4\uc1\pard\f0\fs20 This is a table of the group calendar for accounting purposes (balance sheet date and accounting date by period balance sheet). It must be a distribution on continental sites from Paris.\par
\par
2015-04-22 | OMEGA 2 | EST54 - reported\par
Addition of Column ACCRETSTART_D and ACCRETEND_D (datetime type for both).\par
\par
2017-04-11 | OMEGA 2 | Change request\par
Addition of Column PSTOMGCONEND_D and EBSPSTOMGCONEND_D (datetime type for both).\par
}
</a:Description>
