{\*\generator Msftedit 5.41.21.2510;}\viewkind4\uc1\pard\f0\fs20 Table des utilisateurs\par
PS-le 24/0/02 - modification du TYPE de la civilit\&#39;e9 de TYNINT \&#39;e0 SMALLINT\par
PS-le 12/09/03 - ajout d&#39;une colonne GRPGED_CF\par
V4.1 - Changement du type de TELEDOC_NF : passage de INT \&#39;e0 CHAR(8)\par
V6.1 - Ajout champs pour annuaire d&#39;entreprise (SPOT n\&#39;b012764)\par
\par
2012-01-09 / Omega2\par
- Added column ESB_CF (Reporting ledger code)\par
- Added preferred ledger and subsidiary (PRFSSD_CF and PRFESB_CF)\par
- JOB_CF becomes obsolete\par
\par
2012-01-26 / Omega2\par
- Removed columns NEWCONEX_CT and HRORI_LS, which do not exist in database\par
\par
2012-05-09 / Omega2\par
- Added column PRFGRP_CF\par
- Added column THEME_CT\par
- Modified semantics of GRP_CF (now reporting unit)\par
\par
2012-07-02 / Omega2\par
- Removed useless column PRFGRP_CF\par
2013-06-05/ Omega2 Evocard: TRA03-Phase 1B&#39;\par
-Added column MAINMGRUSR_CF\par
-Added column OUTOFOFF_B\par
-Added column OUTFROM_D\par
-Added column OUTTO_D\par
-Added column MAINREPUSR_CF\par
}
</a:Description>
<a:Annotation>{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg1252\deff0\deflang1033{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset0 Times New Roman;}}
{\*\generator Msftedit 5.41.21.2510;}\viewkind4\uc1\pard\f0\fs20 Users table: we define the main group (and the main subsidiary) and the job of a user.\par
Other user groups are listed in the table TUSRANFN.\par
Users are administered by the administrator of their main subsidiary or respective group administrator.\par
}
</a:Annotation>
