<a:Description>{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg1252\deff0\deflang1036{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset0 Times New Roman;}}
{\*\generator Msftedit 5.41.21.2510;}\viewkind4\uc1\pard\f0\fs20 This table contains the detailled of taxation rules.\par
\par
Different informations are stored in this table such as the taxation rule general information (ledger, Id, etc..) or the context in which the taxation would be valid (Cedent country, Reporting Country, etc..).  \par
\par
