<a:Description>{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg1252\deff0\deflang1036{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset0 Times New Roman;}}
{\*\generator Msftedit 5.41.21.2510;}\viewkind4\uc1\pard\f0\fs20 This table is used to store the list of T. Code related to one taxation rule.\par
\par
For each T. Code included in the scope of application of one taxation rule, informations such as the Tax T. Code or the tax rate are defined. \par
\par
2014-10-28/ Omega2-Phase2C-TAC01-B\par
- Table created\par
}
